task.summary: - added debug message when running pending intent - surround device timeout change with try & catch to prevent crashes on some devices. - removed unnecessary files. - added another sms app to the blacklisted lock screens.
v1.5.1.421 alpha: 1. Improved support for themes (allow changing layouts - supports Android L theme) 2. Extract prominent color. 3. Works now with gradle. 4. Other bug fixes.
v1.5.1.421 alpha2: - Bug fixes - Support prominent color coloring on themes icon background - Support app icon bg on themes - Changed timeout of proximity sensor to 500ms
- added debug messages whenever the screen is turned on - changed auto detection default to false - added SHOW_WHEN_LOCKED flag to OpenNotificationActivity
- handling old values from lock screen detection on NiLS FP
v1.5.1.423: - Fixed unlock issue for LG-G2 - Fixed some crashes on PopupNotification - Support theme custom layouts on preview mode too.
v1.5.1.425: - Fixed crashes - Debug build is now upgradable.
v1.5.1.425: - improved support for Android wear - fixed some crashes - add more debug messages - add some project files to svn
v1.5.1.427: - Added "What's New" for v1.5.1 - Fixed "Show log" on debug version. - Added an option to send a test notification.
